{"id":"p003","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p003-s0","tokens":[{"s":"その"},{"s":"力","r":"ちから","v":"v0088"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"かつて","v":"v0861"},{"s":"騎士団","r":"きしだん","v":"v2206"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"トップクラス","v":"v0460"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"槍術士","r":"そうじゅつし","v":"v2215"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"知ら","r":"しら","v":"v0209","lemma":"知る"},{"s":"れ"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"い"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"頃","r":"ころ","v":"v0016"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"比","r":"ひ","v":"v2216"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"His power was nothing like the days when he'd been known as one of the order's top-class lance-knights.","note":"〜の比ではない = idiom, \"not (even) a comparison to ~\" — used to dismiss a former version of something as far weaker."}}]}
{"id":"p004","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p004-s0","tokens":[{"s":"鋼鉄","r":"こうてつ","v":"v2217"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"棒","r":"ぼう","v":"v1226"},{"s":"すら"},{"s":"捻じ切れる","r":"ねじきれる","v":"v2218"},{"s":"程","r":"ほど","v":"v0311"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"膂力","r":"りょりょく","v":"v2219"},{"s":"から"},{"s":"放た","r":"はなた","v":"v0438","lemma":"放つ"},{"s":"れる"},{"s":"巨大","r":"きょだい","v":"v0933"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"ランス","v":"v1938"},{"s":"型","r":"がた","v":"v2220"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"宝具","r":"ほうぐ","v":"v0083"},{"s":"──"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"風竜閃","r":"ふうりゅうせん","v":"v2221"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"分厚い","r":"ぶあつい","v":"v1082"},{"s":"金属","r":"きんぞく","v":"v1269"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"盾","r":"たて","v":"v1934"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"貫通","r":"かんつう","v":"v2222"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"宝具","r":"ほうぐ","v":"v0083"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"能力","r":"のうりょく","v":"v0585"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"付随","r":"ふずい","v":"v2223"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004"},{"s":"風","r":"かぜ","v":"v0365"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"受け止め","r":"うけとめ","v":"v2224","lemma":"受け止める"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"者","r":"もの","v":"v0244"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"暴風","r":"ぼうふう","v":"v2225"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"蹂躙","r":"じゅうりん","v":"v2182"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The giant lance-type artefact 『Wind-Dragon Flash』, loosed by arms strong enough to twist apart steel rods, drove through thick metal shields; the wind that came with the artefact's power tore through whoever caught the blow with a storm.","note":"膂力 is a literary word for physical strength (compare 力 in everyday usage); used here for the formal action-prose register."}}]}
{"id":"p005","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s0","tokens":[{"s":"優れ","r":"すぐれ","v":"v2226","lemma":"優れる"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"いる"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"攻撃力","r":"こうげきりょく","v":"v2227"},{"s":"だけ"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"It wasn't only his offensive power that excelled."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s1","tokens":[{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"元","r":"もと","v":"v2228"},{"s":"騎士","r":"きし","v":"v1096"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Rodolphe was a former knight."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s2","tokens":[{"s":"その"},{"s":"本領","r":"ほんりょう","v":"v2229"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"防御","r":"ぼうぎょ","v":"v2230"},{"s":"能力","r":"のうりょく","v":"v0585"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"ある","v":"v0095"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"言っ","r":"いっ","v":"v0024","lemma":"言う"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"いい","v":"v0851"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"You could say his real specialty lay in defence."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s3","tokens":[{"s":"身","r":"み","v":"v0521"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"纏っ","r":"まとっ","v":"v1097","lemma":"纏う"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"全身","r":"ぜんしん","v":"v0844"},{"s":"鎧","r":"よろい","v":"v1084"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"宝具","r":"ほうぐ","v":"v0083"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"こそ"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"並","r":"なみ","v":"v2231"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"攻撃","r":"こうげき","v":"v1242"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"傷","r":"きず","v":"v1129"},{"s":"一つ","r":"ひとつ","v":"v0035"},{"s":"つか","v":"v0390","lemma":"つく"},{"s":"ず"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"左手","r":"ひだりて","v":"v2232"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"構え","r":"かまえ","v":"v2233","lemma":"構える"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"盾","r":"たて","v":"v1934"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"合わせれ","r":"あわせれ","v":"v1185","lemma":"合わせる"},{"s":"ば"},{"s":"鉄壁","r":"てっぺき","v":"v2234"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"誇る","r":"ほこる","v":"v0448"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The full plate armour he wore wasn't an artefact, but no ordinary phantom's attack left a scratch on it; combined with the shield in his left hand, it was a wall of iron.","note":"〜でこそない = \"is not (X) per se\" — でこそ adds an emphatic concession (\"not (X) specifically, granted, but…\") that lets the writer concede a point and immediately push past it."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s4","tokens":[{"s":"その"},{"s":"防御","r":"ぼうぎょ","v":"v2230"},{"s":"能力","r":"のうりょく","v":"v0585"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"かの"},{"s":"有名","r":"ゆうめい","v":"v0655"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"《"},{"s":"嘆きの亡霊","r":"なげきのぼうれい","v":"v0178"},{"s":"》"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"その"},{"s":"一員","r":"いちいん","v":"v2235"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"あり"},{"s":"最硬","r":"さいこう","v":"v2236"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"誇る","r":"ほこる","v":"v0448"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"噂","r":"うわさ","v":"v0848"},{"s":"さ","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"れる"},{"s":"《"},{"s":"不動不変","r":"ふどうふへん","v":"v2237"},{"s":"》"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"負け","r":"まけ","v":"v1996","lemma":"負ける"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"い"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"という"},{"s":"自負","r":"じふ","v":"v2238"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"あっ","v":"v0095","lemma":"ある"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"He prided himself that his defensive power didn't fall short even of 《Stillness Unchanging》 — the member rumoured to be the toughest in that famous party 《Lamenting Spectres》.","note":"かの〜 is a literary attributive (\"that famous ~ / that renowned ~\"), more weighty than あの. 自負 = \"a sense of pride in one's own ability\"; the word implies a self-assessment, not external praise."}}]}
{"id":"p006","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p006-s0","tokens":[{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"経験","r":"けいけん","v":"v1590"},{"s":"こそ"},{"s":"浅く","r":"あさく","v":"v2239","lemma":"浅い"},{"s":"まだ"},{"s":"レベル","v":"v0284"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"５"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"この"},{"s":"まま"},{"s":"経験","r":"けいけん","v":"v1590"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"積め","r":"つめ","v":"v2240","lemma":"積む"},{"s":"ば"},{"s":"二つ名","r":"ふたつな","v":"v2241"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"得る","r":"える","v":"v2242"},{"s":"こと","v":"v0120"},{"s":"すら"},{"s":"夢","r":"ゆめ","v":"v0122"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"だろう"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Hunting experience was still shallow and his level only 5, but if he kept piling up experience, even earning a two-name title wasn't out of reach.","note":"二つ名 (\"two-name\") = a heroic byname or epithet earned through deeds, attached to a Hunter's given name as an honorific. The narrator's 《Thousand Trials》 is one such 二つ名."}}]}
{"id":"p007","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p007-s0","tokens":[{"s":"パーティメンバー","v":"v2243"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"自身","r":"じしん","v":"v0942"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"こそ"},{"s":"劣る","r":"おとる","v":"v2244"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"優秀","r":"ゆうしゅう","v":"v2039"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"メンバー","v":"v0233"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"揃っ","r":"そろっ","v":"v0693","lemma":"揃う"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"いる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"His party members fell short of Rodolphe himself — but they were a capable bunch."}}]}
