{"id":"p010","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p010-s0","tokens":[{"s":"特に","r":"とくに","v":"v1399"},{"s":"憂慮","r":"ゆうりょ","v":"v2247"},{"s":"す","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"べき"},{"s":"点","r":"てん","v":"v1415"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"なかっ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Nothing in particular gave him cause for concern."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p010-s1","tokens":[{"s":"レベル","v":"v0284"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"低い","r":"ひくい","v":"v0966"},{"s":"から"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"いっ","v":"v0024","lemma":"いう"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"準備","r":"じゅんび","v":"v2248"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"怠る","r":"おこたる","v":"v2249"},{"s":"ような"},{"s":"こと","v":"v0120"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"なかっ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Just because the level was low didn't mean they cut corners on preparation.","note":"〜からといって〜ない = \"just because (X), it doesn't follow that (Y)\" — denies an inference the reader might otherwise make."}}]}
{"id":"p011","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p011-s0","tokens":[{"s":"最初","r":"さいしょ","v":"v1075"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"順調","r":"じゅんちょう","v":"v2250"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"っ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"At first, things went smoothly."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p011-s1","tokens":[{"s":"現れる","r":"あらわれる","v":"v0212"},{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"軽々","r":"かるがる","v":"v2251"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"屠り","r":"ほふり","v":"v2058","lemma":"屠る"},{"s":"ながら"},{"s":"どんどん","v":"v0308"},{"s":"中","r":"なか","v":"v0109"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"進ん","r":"すすん","v":"v1215","lemma":"進む"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"いっ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Cutting easily through every phantom that appeared, they pressed deeper and deeper."}}]}
{"id":"p012","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p012-s0","tokens":[{"s":"異変","r":"いへん","v":"v2252"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"感じ","r":"かんじ","v":"v2253","lemma":"感じる"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"宝物殿","r":"ほうもつでん","v":"v0027"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"訪れ","r":"おとずれ","v":"v0257","lemma":"訪れる"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"三日目","r":"みっかめ","v":"v2254"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"事","r":"こと","v":"v0120"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"っ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"It was on the third day inside the Treasury that he sensed something off."}}]}
{"id":"p013","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p013-s0","tokens":[{"s":"不意","r":"ふい","v":"v1778"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"現れる","r":"あらわれる","v":"v0212"},{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"レベル","v":"v0284"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"上がり","r":"あがり","v":"v2008","lemma":"上がる"},{"s":"始め","r":"はじめ","v":"v0185","lemma":"始める"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The level of the phantoms appearing began, abruptly, to climb."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p013-s1","tokens":[{"s":"最初","r":"さいしょ","v":"v1075"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ほんの","v":"v2255"},{"s":"些細","r":"ささい","v":"v2256"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"違い","r":"ちがい","v":"v0593"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"っ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"その"},{"s":"差","r":"さ","v":"v1725"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"どんどん","v":"v0308"},{"s":"大きく","r":"おおきく","v":"v0069","lemma":"大きい"},{"s":"なり","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"普段","r":"ふだん","v":"v0905"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"【"},{"s":"白狼","r":"はくろう","v":"v0758"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"巣","r":"す","v":"v0759"},{"s":"】"},{"s":"から"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"考え","r":"かんがえ","v":"v0927","lemma":"考える"},{"s":"られ"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"程","r":"ほど","v":"v0311"},{"s":"強い","r":"つよい","v":"v0044"},{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"現れ","r":"あらわれ","v":"v0212","lemma":"現れる"},{"s":"始め","r":"はじめ","v":"v0185","lemma":"始める"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"At first the gap was trivial, but it kept growing — until phantoms unthinkable for the usual 【White Wolves' Den】 began to appear.","note":"〜から考えられない程 = \"to a degree (one) cannot conceive of from (X).\" The から marks the basis of the impossibility-judgement, not a cause."}}]}
{"id":"p014","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p014-s0","tokens":[{"s":"あえて","v":"v2257"},{"s":"問題","r":"もんだい","v":"v1842"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"挙げる","r":"あげる","v":"v0622"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"なら"},{"s":"ば"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"達","r":"たち","v":"v0817"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"強","r":"つよ","v":"v0044","lemma":"強い"},{"s":"すぎ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"事","r":"こと","v":"v0120"},{"s":"だろう"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"If you wanted to point to a problem, it was that Rodolphe's party was too strong."}}]}
{"id":"p015","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p015-s0","tokens":[{"s":"依頼","r":"いらい","v":"v0492"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"関係","r":"かんけい","v":"v1439"},{"s":"上","r":"じょう","v":"v2258"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"パーティ","v":"v0140"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"一人","r":"ひとり","v":"v0022"},{"s":"足り","r":"たり","v":"v2259","lemma":"足りる"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"状態","r":"じょうたい","v":"v1319"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"っ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"それでも","v":"v2260"},{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"・"},{"s":"ダウー","v":"v2204"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"その"},{"s":"パーティ","v":"v0140"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"レベル","v":"v0284"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"跳ね上がっ","r":"はねあがっ","v":"v2103","lemma":"跳ね上がる"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"達","r":"たち","v":"v0817"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"比較","r":"ひかく","v":"v2261"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"強","r":"つよ","v":"v0044","lemma":"強い"},{"s":"すぎ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Due to the circumstances of the assignment, Rodolphe's party was one member short — but even so, Rodolphe Davout and his party were still too strong, even measured against the suddenly elevated phantoms."}}]}
{"id":"p016","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p016-s0","tokens":[{"s":"初め","r":"はじめ","v":"v1071"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"警戒","r":"けいかい","v":"v0834"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"い"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"それ"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"すぐ","v":"v0486"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"消え","r":"きえ","v":"v1657","lemma":"消える"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"いっ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"He was wary at first, but that wariness quickly faded."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p016-s1","tokens":[{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"レベル","v":"v0284"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"いきなり","v":"v1371"},{"s":"上がる","r":"あがる","v":"v2008"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"確か","r":"たしか","v":"v0294"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"異常","r":"いじょう","v":"v1044"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"こちら"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"強さ","r":"つよさ","v":"v2262"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"それ"},{"s":"以上","r":"いじょう","v":"v0275"},{"s":"なら"},{"s":"ば"},{"s":"問題","r":"もんだい","v":"v1842"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"A sudden surge in phantom levels was certainly anomalous — but as long as their own strength outpaced it, no problem."}}]}
{"id":"p017","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p017-s0","tokens":[{"s":"白銀","r":"はくぎん","v":"v0762"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"毛皮","r":"けがわ","v":"v0764"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"骸骨","r":"がいこつ","v":"v1645"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"被っ","r":"かぶっ","v":"v0526","lemma":"被る"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"異形","r":"いぎょう","v":"v2263"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"ウルフナイト","v":"v1818"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"現れ","r":"あらわれ","v":"v0212","lemma":"現れる"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"時","r":"とき","v":"v0058"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"眉","r":"まゆ","v":"v0680"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"顰め","r":"ひそめ","v":"v0681","lemma":"顰める"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"それ"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"また"},{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"怪力","r":"かいりき","v":"v2264"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"宝具","r":"ほうぐ","v":"v0083"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"そして"},{"s":"仲間","r":"なかま","v":"v0179"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"パーティ","v":"v0140"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"もっ"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"すれ","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"ば"},{"s":"さして","v":"v2265"},{"s":"苦戦","r":"くせん","v":"v2266"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004"},{"s":"ような"},{"s":"相手","r":"あいて","v":"v0704"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"なかっ"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"When a deformed wolf-knight, silver-furred and skull-helmed, appeared, his brow furrowed — but even that, with Rodolphe's strength and his artefact and his party behind him, was no especially difficult opponent.","note":"〜をもってすれば is a literary, formal conditional: \"if one employs ~ / with the use of ~.\" さして〜ない = \"not particularly ~,\" also bookish. Both belong in the formal narrative register of this chapter.","grammar":["g-wo-motte-sureba"]}}]}
{"id":"p018","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p018-s0","tokens":[{"s":"さすが","v":"v2029"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"異常事態","r":"いじょうじたい","v":"v2267"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"気づい","r":"きづい","v":"v0535","lemma":"気づく"},{"s":"て"},{"s":"い"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"He had, of course, noticed something was off."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p018-s1","tokens":[{"s":"だ"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"もともと","v":"v0871"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"予定","r":"よてい","v":"v2268"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"後","r":"あと","v":"v0672"},{"s":"一日","r":"いちにち","v":"v0271"},{"s":"探索","r":"たんさく","v":"v0374"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"たら"},{"s":"帝都","r":"ていと","v":"v0335"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"帰る","r":"かえる","v":"v1601"},{"s":"予定","r":"よてい","v":"v2268"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"まだ"},{"s":"力","r":"ちから","v":"v0088"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"余裕","r":"よゆう","v":"v1720"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"ある","v":"v0095"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"But the original plan was one more day of exploration before returning to the imperial capital, and they still had strength to spare."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p018-s2","tokens":[{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"数瞬","r":"すうしゅん","v":"v2269"},{"s":"迷っ","r":"まよっ","v":"v2122","lemma":"迷う"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"即座","r":"そくざ","v":"v2270"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"依頼","r":"いらい","v":"v0492"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"継続","r":"けいぞく","v":"v2271"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"決定","r":"けってい","v":"v2272"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Rodolphe hesitated a moment, then immediately decided to continue the assignment."}}]}
{"id":"p019","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p019-s0","tokens":[{"s":"そして"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"探索","r":"たんさく","v":"v0374"},{"s":"最終日","r":"さいしゅうび","v":"v2273"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"And so — on the last day of exploration."}},{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p019-s1","tokens":[{"s":"ロドルフ","v":"v1958"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"出会っ","r":"であっ","v":"v0710","lemma":"出会う"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Rodolphe met it."}}]}
{"id":"p020","sentences":[{"id":"05-nageki-no-bourei-1-p020-s0","tokens":[{"s":"完全","r":"かんぜん","v":"v0251"},{"s":"なる"},{"s":"人骨","r":"じんこつ","v":"v2274"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"被る","r":"かぶる","v":"v0526"},{"s":"小型","r":"こがた","v":"v2275"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"ウルフナイト","v":"v1818"},{"s":"──"},{"s":"シルバームーン","v":"v2148"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"怨念","r":"おんねん","v":"v2276"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"化身","r":"けしん","v":"v2277"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"A small wolf-knight wearing a complete human skull — the embodied curse of the Silvermoons.","note":"怨念の化身 = \"incarnation of resentment.\" 化身 is a literary/religious word for an avatar or embodied form — used here to render the wolf-knight as something more than a mere phantom. Closes the chapter on the same image that ended chapter 4."}}]}
